   </oasis:tgroup><?xmltex \end{scaleboxenv}?></oasis:table><?xmltex \begin{scaleboxenv}{.95}[.95]?><table-wrap-foot><p id="d1e1720"><?xmltex \hack{\vspace{2mm}}?><inline-formula><mml:math id="M59" display="inline"><mml:msup><mml:mi/><mml:mo>*</mml:mo></mml:msup></mml:math></inline-formula>Â For FAME-C, the cloud
